                  <zone forceUpdate='true' h='26439' id='28' type-v2='text' w='32073' x='67356' y='72561'>
                    <formatted-text>
                      <run bold='true' fontcolor='#000000' fontname='Helvetica' fontsize='11'>Key Insight</run>
                      <run>Æ&#10;&#10;</run>
                      <run fontcolor='#000000' fontname='Helvetica' fontsize='11'>Attrition is concentrated in specific employee segments, especially employees with overtime, sales roles, frequent travel, low income, low job involvement, and short tenure. Retention strategies should prioritize workload control, early-tenure support, and targeted incentives for high-risk roles.</run>
                    </formatted-text>
